WHO   — Little Henry — the last shot
WHAT  — The recoil of the cycle: not a villain but the terrible consequence of the hatred the brothers spread, returning.
WHERE — AHX · American History X (1998)  Framework inputs: American History X (1998, dir. Tony Kaye, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film ends not with redemption but with the cost — hate's violence coming back around.
HOW   — By answering Danny's earlier antagonism with a gun, completing the cycle the film refuses to let anyone escape.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am not the lesson and not the villain. I am what the hatred they spread comes home as — and it comes home too soon.

